description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 43, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 86, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Box for East, 3 for South, and 2 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30432-54321-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [86 Votes, Common]
